  "texts": [
    "The distribution of correct responses by days and platforms is shown in Fig. 2.The analysis showed that ChatGPT-4o provided 86.2% correct responses, 2.9% incorrect responses, and 10.9% insufficient responses.",
    "On the other hand, Gemini offered 48% correct responses, 17.5% incorrect responses, and 34.5% insufficient responses.",
    "In contrast, ChatGPT-4 with the PDF plugin exhibited superior performance by delivering 98.1% correct responses, 1.9% insufficient responses, and no incorrect responses.",
    "DiscussionThe integration of AI technologies in healthcare facilitates the workflow of healthcare professionals and helps in the faster and more accurate treatment of patients [22].",
    "However, since clinical reasoning is typically acquired through multiple years of education and experience, the idea that AI technologies could replace clinicians should be discussed in depth [24]."
